    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Closed-circuit television system where programs are transmitted via coaxial or fiber-optic cable (as opposed to airwave transmissions) to connected subscribers. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
